Bundle-Description: The Apache Commons Codec package contains simple enc
 oder and decoders for     various formats such as Base64 and Hexadecima
 l.  In addition to these     widely used encoders and decoders, the cod
 ec package also maintains a     collection of phonetic encoding utiliti
 es.
